ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is mandatory, but for sure it is necessary to understand fully this course for everyone. Macroeconomics contains a very wide and general, which means important, questions. By understanging it and connecting with what each of us is concerned with, whatever it is, we can proceed to more detailed study on it to yield fruitful and meaningful research.
yes definitely recommend to another student

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It provides us with a general concern of overall economics and how it should be related to our own interest of research. Moreover, it also offers some theoretical tool to analyze the continuous time dynamics, linearization of complex systems, and so on.
great. it will be super helpful to my future research
